description: Outstanding Opportunity! Live in the majestic Monks Building! This impeccable floor through two bedroom, one bathroom residence is exactly what you have been dreaming about! Sunshine is everywhere from the expansive windows! Primary Bedroom with ornate period Carrara marble mantel and large custom built closet! Generous Guest Bedroom with two oversized closets! Enormous & Elegant Open Living room/Dining room with fireplace! A perfect floor plan for memorable entertaining! Gourmet Chef's Kitchen with designer curved breakfast bar, Viking 5-burner stove, abundant cabinetry and sleek stone counters! Gleaming Oak floors! Towering Ceiling Height throughout! Luxurious lavish spa bathroom has been renovated with a beautiful shower with tiled surround, glass shower door and mosaic floor. Great functionality, character and charm! Wonderful 5 panel antique doors! Perched high above the street, this is an elevated first floor unit. In-unit laundry and additional storage! Welcome Home!
